{}^nP_r = \frac {n!} {(n-r)!}
1 + {{}^nP_2}/2 +{{}^nP_3}/3 + ~........... ~ {}^nP_n/n  
= 1 + \frac {n! }{2.(n-2)!} + \frac {n! }{3.(n-3)!} + ........ + \frac {n! }{n.(n-n)!}
